---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Mizan Score Kya Hai - Understanding Our Rating System | Mizan"
  description="Learn how Mizan calculates health scores for packaged foods using FSSAI's Indian Nutrition Rating algorithm."
>
  <article class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">

      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-mizan-teal">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">›</span>
        <a href="/samjho" class="hover:text-mizan-teal">Samjho</a>
        <span class="mx-2">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700">Mizan Score</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-5xl">⭐</span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-2">
          Mizan Score Kya Hai
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-mizan-teal">Understanding Our Rating System</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">3 min read</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Mizan Score ek 1-5 star rating hai jo FSSAI ke Indian Nutrition Rating (INR) algorithm pe based hai.
          Ye scientifically calculate hota hai — koi opinion nahi, sirf math.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Star Ratings</h2>

        <div class="space-y-4 my-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-green-safe/10 rounded-lg border border-green-safe/30">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-accent">5★</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Grade A</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"> — Excellent choice. Low in harmful nutrients.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-green-safe/5 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-accent">4★</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Grade B</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"> — Good choice. Minor concerns.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-amber-warning/10 rounded-lg border border-amber-warning/30">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-accent">3★</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Grade C</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"> — Average. Consume in moderation.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-amber-warning/20 rounded-lg border border-amber-warning/50">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-accent">2★</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Grade D</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"> — Below average. Limit consumption.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-red-critical/10 rounded-lg border border-red-critical/30">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-gold-accent">1★</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Grade F</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"> — Poor choice. High in harmful nutrients.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Calculation Method</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Score do parts mein calculate hota hai:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
          <div class="bg-red-critical/5 border border-red-critical/20 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-red-critical mb-2">Baseline Points (Bad)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Ye points add hote hain:</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Energy (calories)</li>
              <li>• Sodium</li>
              <li>• Sugar</li>
              <li>• Saturated Fat</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Higher = worse</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-safe/10 border border-green-safe/30 rounded-xl p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-green-safe mb-2">Modifying Points (Good)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Ye points subtract hote hain:</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Protein</li>
              <li>• Fiber</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Higher = better</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 my-6">
          <p class="text-center text-gray-700">
            <strong>Final Score</strong> = Baseline Points − Modifying Points
          </p>
          <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
            Lower final score = More stars
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Kya Mizan Score Perfect Hai?</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Nahi. Koi bhi single number poori picture nahi de sakta. Isliye hum ye bhi dikhate hain:
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Roz ki Hadd</strong> — Safe daily serving limit</li>
          <li><strong>Limiting Factors</strong> — Konsa nutrient problem hai</li>
          <li><strong>Mizan ka Faisla</strong> — Plain language verdict</li>
          <li><strong>Full Nutrition</strong> — Complete breakdown</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-mizan-teal/10 border border-mizan-teal/30 rounded-xl p-6 mt-10">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-mizan-teal mb-3">Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Humare saare calculations open source hain. Algorithm dekho, verify karo, improve karo.
          </p>
          <a href="https://github.com/atul-feyntech/mizan-india" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-3 text-mizan-teal hover:underline font-medium">
            View on GitHub →
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 flex justify-between">
        <a href="/samjho/label-padhna" class="text-mizan-teal hover:underline">← Label Padhna</a>
        <a href="/samjho/icmr-guidelines" class="text-mizan-teal hover:underline">Next: ICMR Guidelines →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
